{"tid":1536862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［真人真事］有朋友被私刑","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:22:06.000Z","uid":317633,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d1d007e3afabbef57385451229e33cf1c590a5","tid":1536862,"uid":317633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"我朋友比人捉左去<br />\n唔洗講比人捉得<br />\n都一定私刑化 新屋嶺都知咩事<br />\n詳情唔多講 怕連累到佢<br />\n佢自己都唔敢講出黎<br />\n睇新聞可能見到咁多人被濫用私刑 係香港人都心痛<br />\n但發生係我朋友身上 真係唔敢想像<br />\n當下即刻崩潰 心理壓力好大<br />\n我依家只係想佢快d好返 挨落去<br />\n我出post既目的只係想講 <br />\n日日睇新聞都係果d野 真係好負面 每日心情都好沉重<br />\n1個好好暑假比林鄭仆街搞到咁 縱容黑落行使暴力<br />\n自問好佩服前線勇武 因為我朋友都係其中一個<br />\n就算依家殺左黑警 核彈都唔會割 佢地係抵撚死<br />\n曾經諗過了結生命 聽到我朋友咁樣 佢都挨到<br />\n點解我要白白去為左呢個極權政府去了結生命 唔值得<br />\n各位手足呢場仗仲有排打 好好活著<br />\n所以兄弟爬山 各自努力<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n黑警死全家 禍必及妻兒<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"5123f8616a7a7d850d75ab25a88bcd8112ea37d8","tid":1536862,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eefb774329f6a59dbcf6ccd57d3a99824475c4f","tid":1536862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"女仔？"},{"pid":"d02300835fb1a8bb95037b92de3325180d157f8a","tid":1536862,"uid":251154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"天佑你個好朋友"},{"pid":"45da4384d1f4a716988d2cf286d33849da0e3bef","tid":1536862,"uid":317633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2eefb774329f6a59dbcf6ccd57d3a99824475c4f","tid":1536862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"女仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"男仔 比人打到 一郁 d骨都痛"},{"pid":"b77043b21ec553167dcd606aabc742809662655b","tid":1536862,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"9690ebddc383ff467b712d32939f1e26ebb71871","tid":1536862,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"去驗傷<br />\n搵片證明被捕前後無傷<br />\n但係放出黎/保釋之後 有嚴重受傷"},{"pid":"e61747b6a80e989daf4a33c7dac4941e47a8621f","tid":1536862,"uid":186800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:56:33.000Z","msg":"詳情唔請 咁你開黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206a6bf2442ef1613937f5b0ae0546495ef73c7c","tid":1536862,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"